text: Rita Razmaitė (born 20 June 1967) is a Lithuanian former cyclist. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Lithuania Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kretinga
